{
  "chapter": 70,
  "chapter_summary": "上官金虹因独子上官飞被杀，要与李寻欢决一死战。李寻欢以心情不佳为由推辞，并婉拒了上官金虹的敬酒，两人惺惺相惜，各自离去。上官金虹回到金钱帮总部，将上官飞的尸体展示给阿飞，阿飞坦然承认自己是凶手。上官金虹不杀阿飞，反令吕总管以酒色折磨他，要让他活着痛苦却又没有勇气死。阿飞开口要吕总管的老婆，令众人震惊。李寻欢在夜市独饮，偶遇昔日名剑客吕凤先，见他已沦为酒鬼，痛苦不堪。吕凤先因林仙儿的背叛而心如死灰，想要咬掉自己曾经引以为傲的手。李寻欢劝他回家疗伤，身后却传来神秘人的问话。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "无论什么时候我都奉陪，只有今天不行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "今天我……我只想去喝杯酒。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "有些时候非但不适合决斗，也不适合做别的事，除了喝酒外，几乎什么事都不能做，今天就是这种时候。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "那么，你说什么时候？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "我早已说过，无论什么时候。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我到哪里找你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "你用不着找我，只要你说，我就会去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我说了，你能听到？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "上官帮主说出来的话，天下皆闻，我想听不到都很难。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你要喝酒，这里有酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "这里的酒我配喝么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你若不配，就没有第二个人配了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我敬你一杯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "好酒！好痛快的酒！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "二十年来，这是我第一次喝酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "上官金虹若不是上官金虹，又何尝不会是我的好朋友？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "卿本佳人，奈何做贼？……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "旁人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "李寻欢果然不愧是李寻欢，放眼天下，也只有李寻欢才能要上官帮主敬他一杯酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "旁人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜他们没有真的打起来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "旁人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我总觉得这两人像是有些相同的地方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "旁人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "李寻欢和上官金虹会有相同之处？……你疯了么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "旁人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们的作风和行事虽然完全不同，可是他们……他们全都不是人，他们做的事，如果'是人'就绝对做不到的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "旁人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这话倒有几分道理，他们的确都不是人，只不过——一个是仙佛，一个却是恶魔。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "旁人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，李寻欢若不是李寻欢，也许就是另一个上官金虹。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "像这么样站着，你不觉得难受么？为什么不舒舒服服地坐下来，我旁边就有张椅子。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你不肯坐？我也知道你坐不住的，在这里坐着实在不是滋味。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "可是你为什么又不走呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我虽然挡着门，但你随时都可以将我打倒的呀，要不然，那边有窗子，你也可以像小偷一样跳窗子逃出去，这两种法子都容易得很。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你不敢？是不是？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你心里虽然恨不得杀了我，可是你还是不敢动手，甚至连碰都不敢碰我，因为你心里还是在爱着我的，是不是？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "回过头来，看看这人是谁！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你认得他，是不是？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "他几天前还活着的，而且活得很好，是不是？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "现在你忽然看到他死了，也未吃惊，只因你早就知道他死了，是不是？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "不错，我的确早就知道他死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你怎会知道的？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "因为杀死他的人，就是我！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你在等死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你承认，为的就是希望我杀死你，是么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lv_zong_guan",
      "text": "吕总管。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_zong_guan",
      "speaker_name": "吕总管",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "属下在。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "他要死，我们不给他死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_zong_guan",
      "speaker_name": "吕总管",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lv_zong_guan",
      "text": "我们给他别的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_zong_guan",
      "speaker_name": "吕总管",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lv_zong_guan",
      "text": "给他酒，给他女人，他要多少，就给多少。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_zong_guan",
      "speaker_name": "吕总管",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lv_zong_guan",
      "text": "他无论要谁，都给他！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_zong_guan",
      "speaker_name": "吕总管",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_zong_guan",
      "speaker_name": "吕总管",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "无论谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lv_zong_guan",
      "text": "无论谁都一样，就算他要你的老婆，也给他！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_zong_guan",
      "speaker_name": "吕总管",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "属下明白了，属下这就去将老婆带来给他看。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "他若要我呢？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我说过，无论谁都一样。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "可是……可是我却不一样，我是你的，除了你，谁都不能……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "无论谁都可以要你，为什么他不可以？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_lv_zong_guan",
      "text": "我要什么都给他，就是不能让他走，我要看他三个月后会变成什么样子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_zong_guan",
      "speaker_name": "吕总管",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "我杀了你儿子，你为什么不杀我？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "因为我要让你活着痛苦，又没有勇气死！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_zong_guan",
      "speaker_name": "吕总管",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "人生得意须尽欢，莫使金樽空对月。做人本就是这么回事，又何必太认真呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_zong_guan",
      "speaker_name": "吕总管",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还不快为飞少爷置酒？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_zong_guan",
      "speaker_name": "吕总管",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "喝吧，酒喝得多了，你就会发觉世上所有的女人本都是一样的，不必认真。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lv_zong_guan",
      "text": "不一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_zong_guan",
      "speaker_name": "吕总管",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "那么你要的是谁呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lv_zong_guan",
      "text": "我要你的老婆！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "花木纵无情，迟早也凋零，无情的人，也总有一日憔悴。人若无情，活着还有何滋味？纵然在无人处暗弹相思泪，也总比无泪可流好几倍。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_bu_lao_tou",
      "speaker_name": "油布老头",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "酒鬼，不要脸，偷酒喝，就算你喝下去我也要你吐出来！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_you_bu_lao_tou",
      "text": "让他喝酒，算我的钱。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "一个人独饮最无趣，我那边还有下酒的菜，何妨过去一起喝几杯？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你是什么东西？你配跟我一起喝酒？就算你再买三百坛酒送给我，也休想要我陪你……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "你……是你？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "等一等，等一等……兄台莫非不认得小弟了么？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我不认得你，我不喝你的酒……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "旁人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那偷酒的人原来是个疯子，明知要挨揍也敢来偷酒喝，但等到别人请喝酒时，他反而逃了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "旁人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那买酒的人更疯，既花了钱，又挨了骂，还要称那人为兄台，像这种人我倒真没有瞧见过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你为什么不让我走？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我本不欠你的，本不必为你做什么事，你何必还要来逼我？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "我欠你的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "就算你欠我，也不必还。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "我欠你的，本就无法还，但你至少也该让我请你喝杯酒。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "莫忘了，你也请过我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "放开我，我要咬掉它，一口口嚼碎，一口口吞下去！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 594,
      "line_end": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "若是别人做了对不起你的事，该死的是他，你又何苦折磨自己？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "该死的是我，我自己……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "你何必还留在这里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 624,
      "line_end": 626
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "不留在这里，到哪里去？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 630,
      "line_end": 630
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "回去，回家去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 632
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "家？……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 634,
      "line_end": 634
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "你现在就好像生了场大病，这病只有两种药能治好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "两种药？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 638
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "第一种是家，第二种是时间，你只要回家……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 640
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我不回家。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 644,
      "line_end": 644
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "因为……因为那已不是我的家了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 646,
      "line_end": 646
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "家就是家，永远都不会变的，这就是家的可贵。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 648,
      "line_end": 648
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "speaker_name": "吕凤先",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "就算永远没有变，我却已变了，我已经不是我。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 650,
      "line_end": 652
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_lv_feng_xian",
      "text": "你若肯在家里安安静静地过一段时候，就一定会变回原来的你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 654,
      "line_end": 656
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘人",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "若是没有家的人，这种病是不是就永远也不会治好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 658,
      "line_end": 660
    }
  ],
